import { Flex, VStack } from "@chakra-ui/react"

const Login = () => {
    return (
        <Flex>
            <VStack>
                <FormControl>
                    <FormLabel htmlFor='username'>Username</FormLabel>
                    <Input type='text' />
                </FormControl>
                <FormControl>
                    <FormLabel htmlFor='username'>Username</FormLabel>
                    <Input type='text' />
                </FormControl>
            </VStack>
        </Flex>
    )
}

export default Login
